下类型的个人信息：</span></span></p><p style=font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>1、完成注册、登录及注销</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><br></span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>为便于我们提供服务，未成年人需要提供基本注册或登录信息，</span></span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>包括手机号码、电子邮箱地址，并创建有道精品课服务账号、用户名和密码</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>。如果仅需使用浏览、搜索等基本服务，未成年人不需要注册成为有道精品课用户及提供上述信息。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0 0 10px;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;line-height:27px;background:#fff"><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>在</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>有道精品课服务</span></span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>注册及登录过程中，如果未成年人提供其他额外信息（包括</span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>性别、出生年月日、兴趣爱好、学习阶段、学习目标</span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>），将有助于我们为其提供个性化的推荐和更优的服务体验，但如果不提供这些信息，并不会影响其使用有道精品课服务的基本功能。同时，</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>依照相关法律</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>法规</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>的</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>实名</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>要求</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>或者特定功能及服务需要</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>，</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>我们可能</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>需要</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>未成年人和</span>/或监护人提供其他信息（包括</span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>姓名、身份证、面部特征</span></strong><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>或其他身份证明信息</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>）。</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>如果不提供</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>上述</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>信息，我们</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>将</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>不能向</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>其</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>提供相关的功能</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>及服务。</span></p><p style="margin:0 0 10px;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;line-height:27px;background:#fff"><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>此外，在符合有道精品课服务的服务协议约定条件及国家相关法律法规规定的情况下，我们也提供未成年人注册账号的注销，未成年人和监护人可以</span><a name=_Hlk49873915></a></span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>自行</span></span></strong><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>按照本政策的约定完成注销。</span></span></strong></p><p style=font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px>2、提供产品或服务</span></p><p style=font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>（</span>1）未成年人在使用有道精品课服务时、上传和/或发布信息以及进行相关行为时，我们将收集未成年人上传、发布或形成的信息，并有权展示未成年人的昵称、头像和发布内容<a name=OLE_LINK55></a><a name=OLE_LINK54></a><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>。</span></span></p><p style=font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>（</span>2）在部分服务项目中，为便于向未成年人交付产品或服务，未成年人</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>可能</span></span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>需提供</span></span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>收货人个人身份信息、姓名、收货地址、邮政编码、收货人、联系电话、支付状态信息</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>。如果拒绝提供此类信息，我们将无法为其提供交付服务。</span></span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>未成年人在</span></span></strong><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>向我们或我们的合作伙伴购买产品或服务之前，需确保已经取得监护人的授权同意</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>。</span></span></p><p style=font-size:medium;text-indent:0;white-space:normal><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>（</span>3）为展示未成年人账户的订单信息及保障未成年人的售后权益，</span><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>我们会收集您在使用有道精品课服务过程中产生的</span></span><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>订单信息、交易和消费记录、虚拟财产信息</span></span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>用于向未成年人展示及便于其对订单进行管理。</span></span></p><p style=font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>（</span>4）当未成年人与我们联系时，我们可能会保存未成年人的</span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>通信</span>/通话记录和内容或未成年人留下的联系方式</span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>等信息，以便与未成年人或监护人联系或帮助其解决问题，或记录相关问题的处理方案及结果。</span></span></p><p style=font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>（</span>5）为确认交易状态及为未成年人提供售后与争议解决服务，我们会通过未成年人基于交易所选择的交易对象、支付机构、物流公司等收集与交易进度相关的</span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>交易、支付、物流信息</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>，或将其</span></span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>交易信息</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>共享给上述服务提供者。</span></span></p><p style=font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:27px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;color:#222;font-size:14px;background:#fcfcfc>3、维护基础功能的政策运行</span></p><p style=font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;margin-top:15px;margin-bottom:15px;line-height:22px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>在未成年人使用我们服务过程中，为识别账号异常状态、了解产品适配性，向未成年人提供浏览、搜索等基本服务，维护基础功能的正常运行，</span></span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>我们可能会自动收集、储存关于</span></span></strong><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>未成年</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>人</span></span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>使用的服务以及使用方式的信息并将这些信息进行关联，这些信息包括：</span></span></strong></p><p style=text-align:justify;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;line-height:22px><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>（</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff>1</span></span></strong><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>）日志信息</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>：当</span></span></strong><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>未成年</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>人</span></span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>使用我们的服务时，我们可能会自动收集</span></span></strong><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>未成年</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>人</span></span><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>对我们服务的详细使用情况，作为有关网络日志保存。日志信息包括</span></span></strong><strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>未成年</span></span></strong><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>人</span></span><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>的登录账号、搜索查询内容、</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff>IP</span></span></strong><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>地址、浏览器的类型、电信运营商、网络环境、使用的语言、访问日期和时间及</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>未成年人</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff><span style=font-family:微软雅黑>访问的网页浏览记录、</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;background:#fff>Push</span></span></strong><strong><span style=text-decoration:underline><span style=font-f